profile:
Halton Handyman provides a one-stop-shop solution for clients in need of house repairs, renos, improvements, and installation services. I have built up client trust through providing exceptional customer service experiences and maintaining that trust with every visit. The services include consultation as well as the execution of projects promptly. Halton Handyman understands the importance of paying attention to detail to make it done right and remain within the client's budget. 

Services Provided:
Repairs, Upgrades, and Installation
Painting and Decorating
Flooring and Tiling
Renovations and mush more. 

EXPERIENCE & KNOWLEDGE
I combine quality workmanship, superior knowledge and low prices to provide you with service unmatched by other competitors.

BEST MATERIALS
My project management experience combined with my construction knowledge and skills will make the project run smoothly. I will ensure that the job is done right in timely manner.

PROFESSIONAL STANDARDS
My project management process involve a carefully planned series of steps, centred around a schedule I stick to and communicate daily with client about the on going progress.

If these are important to you as well then kindly give me a call and we'll see what Halton Handyman could do for you and your family.
Halton Handyman Team

profile:
At Silicone Seals, our goal is to make sure you get quality service for what you need.
 We specialize in a variety of services to take care of the big and small things your home needs.
 Whether you need sealant in your bathroom, or caulking around windows and doors, we got you covered.

We believe that our exceptional customer service, and quality work makes many happy customers. Contact us today to get a FREE QUOTE for your home.
services:
Our Primary Services:

- replacing caulking that is moldy and falling apart in your bathroom or kitchen

- caulking and sealing around masonry, concrete, decking/porch, and foundations

- draft sealing (foaming), using the highest quality low, medium, and high expansion foam and insulations, from todays leading manufactures. Let us get rid of those cold air drafts inside your home, and get you winter ready

- repairing or replacing caulking around windows and doors, using the highest grade of, silicone, polyurethane, acrylic or elastomeric sealants 

- caulking new windows and doors (new construction or installation) 

- Indoor and outdoor 

We also specialize in:
- repairing Interior water/moisture damage due to failed caulking or leaks, including drywall, ceiling, and floor repair.

- window and door trim repair.

- weather striping and threshold installation 

- stud and joist repair/replacing. Painting/repainting damaged or new surfaces. 

- epoxy and acrylic sealers over concrete, masonry, hardscaping and many other surfaces 

- restoring, staining and sealing wooden decks, fences, gazebos and docks 

- power washing and refreshing old masonry and concrete 

- we also offer grading and hardscaping as part of improving your homes water diversion, and prevent icing. Including, limestone screening, weed barrier, gravel, HPB, decorative river/quarry rock, interlocking, retaining wall, (both masonry, and lumber) and flag stone repairs and installation.
warranty_terms: Yes. Kindly ask for details. Depends on project completed.

profile:
Welcome to Corcoran Construction!

A licensed, bonded and insured Contractor with the City of Hamilton and over 25 years of experience, Corcoran Construction can help you with any job, big or small: Full scale construction projects or small household repairs.

Your needs will be met with the utmost professionalism. We are built on courteous, polite service, and open communication. Corcoran Construction ensures your project will run stress free right from the start with returning messages quickly and showing up ON TIME. 

Sometimes large companies can be daunting to call, when all you need is a couple of hours to repair something. Bigger companies can also be an issue for large scale projects, with the lead sub-contracting others to do the job. Rest assured, Ed Corcoran will be the person on the phone, at your door and at your home or construction site. The job isn’t done until both parties are satisfied! 

Being particular about a job well done is something you would hope to see in all lines of work, especially when it comes to work done in your home or business space. 
Ed Corcoran is at the top of his profession with not only his exceptional work ethics and project creations, but his applied creativity and problem-solving skills- which are a necessity in this field. 

No need to call anyone else either – Ed has top notch professionals in every field at his fingertips waiting for his call should you need additional services to your project such as electrical or painting.

Don’t be disappointed ever again. Make one more call to Corcoran Construction and it will be the last one you need to make!


General Contractor & Handyman Services
    Ed Corcoran    -Master Carpenter 
    corcoranconstruction77@gmail.com 
    289-527-3146

With more than 15 years of experience, Pesantez Painting provides a high quality painting and finishing services for residential clients across southern Ontario. We pride ourselves in our personalised service to ensure customer satisfaction. This is reflected in the growth of our business and the referrals we receive from our satisfied customers. Don’t forget to check our Facebook page so you can see what our customers are saying.

We are contractors specialized in texturized or popcorn ceiling removal, interior and exterior residential painting, drywall and taping, fence and deck refinishing and staining, and water damage repairing. For previous jobs and tutorials, check out our blog.

We serve Hamilton and surrounding cities, up to 40 km. However, we are happy to provide you with a free quote if you live outside our regular area, after considering transportation costs.

profile:
At Family Man Handy man we are very professional with what we do, and we give you piece of mind knowing that the job will be done right the first time.

With over 60 years of combined experience between us, there isn’t much we haven’t seen. 

We care about the little details and have an eye for perfection.
  

We believe that a homeowner may want to do the work themselves, but is lacking the tools, skills, knowledge, or expertise to do the job. If you are willing to provide some labor then why shouldn't you save some money? Maybe you’re just way too busy? Our team is flexible to your schedule. Weekend and evening service is available. Work alongside with us as we fix your problems, or leave it all up to us. Best of all, we offer a low hourly rate for the small jobs with a minimum of 2 hours. Or for the larger jobs we offer a low daily rate. Contact us today for a FREE quote. Remember, no job is too small for us.


We are very passionate about our work.
We are clean and use drop sheets all through the work area.
We are licensed, bonded, and fully insured with WSIB and have 2 million liability insurance.
